　　　　　　　檢察官  周文祥\r\n本件證明與原本無異\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　 109　　年　　11　　月　　9 　　日\r\n                              書記官  鍾明智","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/109%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c3314%2c20201130%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,109,交簡,3314,20201130,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"3314","JDATE":"20201130","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}